		title: "The Living Canopy"
		icon: {id: "ars_nouveau:archwood_log", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Archwood trees generate in their own glowing clearings — faintly luminescent, unmistakable once you know what to look for. Every Ars Nouveau recipe in this chapter traces back to this wood.", "If you can't find a clearing, plant Source Berry Bushes near each other in a forest. The environment will do the rest eventually. Or just keep walking — they're out there."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000000B002"
			type: "item"
