		title: "The Apprentice"
		icon: {id: "ars_nouveau:apprentice_spellbook", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Apprentice Spellbook holds more spells and allows longer glyph chains — a spell that slows a target, deals cold damage, and pulls it toward you is a single keybind from this book.", "Craft it at the Scribes Table. The glyph slot count opens up. Start building real combinations."]
