		x: 0.0d
		y: 2.0d
		title: "The World Breathes"
		icon: {id: "naturesaura:eye_of_nature", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Nature's Aura treats the world as a living energy system. Every biome holds a reserve of Aura — invisible, finite, slowly regenerating. Drain it too fast and the land goes quiet.", "The Eye of Nature shows you the local Aura level as a number on screen. Craft one. Don't let it hit zero near your base."]
