		title: "The Natural Altar"
		icon: {id: "naturesaura:natural_altar", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Natural Altar is Nature's Aura's crafting station — no GUI, no fuel slot. Place ingredients on top, throw the catalyst, and it pulls Aura from the environment to complete the recipe.", "Surround it with trees. Trees feed Aura into the area. Clear-cutting near your Altar is how you make it stop working."]
