		icon: {id: "naturesaura:aura_bottle", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Aura Bottles capture ambient Aura for later — release one in a depleted zone to restore the local level, or use them as crafting ingredients in higher-tier Altar recipes.", "Fill glass bottles in a dense old-growth forest or jungle. Never fill them in your base biome if you're already running low."]
