		description: ["Sky Ingots are Nature's Aura's primary crafting metal — made at the Natural Altar from gold and lightning-struck materials. They feed into the mod's more powerful tools, structures, and passive Aura generators.", "Place iron blocks outside during a thunderstorm. Lightning strikes them. That's your lightning-touched material. The world does the work."]
